                                 Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Just a few of the reasons you'll love HandBrake.

Get started with HandBrake in seconds by choosing a profile optimised for your 
device, or choose a universal profile for standard or high quality conversions. 
Simple, easy, fast. For those that want more choice, tweak many basic and 
advanced options to improve your encodes.


Supported Input Sources:
Handbrake can process most common multimedia files and any DVD or BluRay sources 
that do not contain any kind of copy protection.

Outputs:

File Containers: .MP4(.M4V) and .MKV
Video Encoders: H.264(x264), MPEG-4 and MPEG-2 (libav), and Theora(libtheora)
Audio Encoders: AAC, CoreAudio AAC/HE-AAC (OS X Only), MP3, Flac, AC3, or Vorbis
Audio Pass-thru: AC-3, DTS, DTS-HD, AAC and MP3 tracks

Even more features

Title / Chapter selection
Queue up multiple encodes
Chapter Markers
Subtitles (VobSub, Closed Captions CEA-608, SSA, SRT)
Constant Quality or Average Bitrate Video Encoding
Support for VFR, CFR and VFR
Video Filters: Deinterlacing, Decomb, Detelecine, Deblock, Grayscale, Cropping 
and scaling
Live Video Preview
